Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.24,0:00:09.89,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,That was loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.89,0:00:11.63,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Haru, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.63,0:00:13.32,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,My late grandma used to say
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.57,0:00:16.73,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,that you sneeze when someone \Nelse is talking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.77,0:00:16.73,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.40,0:00:20.08,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,It must be Rin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.58,0:00:23.78,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm pretty sure he's just sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.78,0:00:26.13,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you were swimming \Nin the pool in April.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.49,0:00:28.42,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a baby that gets sick from swimmi—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.36,0:00:32.31,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early for swimming in outdoor pools.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.31,0:00:34.27,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just have to work out until it's warmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.27,0:00:36.22,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I heard from Gou-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.60,0:00:38.93,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,that Rin-chan joined the \NSamezuka swim team.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.69,0:00:40.30,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.30,0:00:41.82,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong, Mako-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.42,0:00:46.41,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.41,0:00:49.20,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,But this means we might run \Ninto him in a tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.20,0:00:50.98,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, we should enter tournaments!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.28,0:00:52.99,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Then we can do relays again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.53,0:00:55.21,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I only swim freestyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.21,0:00:57.59,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean you can't swim relays?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.59,0:01:00.25,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.28,0:01:03.00,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.00,0:01:05.97,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, we can't swim a \Nrelay with three people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.61,0:01:07.78,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.78,0:01:09.71,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.04,0:01:13.22,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,We have to find one more member?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.99,0:02:48.34,EpTitle,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(383,464)}Theoretical Dolphin Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:50.48,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,We need one more member.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:53.31,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,But it'll be hard to find one now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:02:56.22,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,I was turned down by everyone \NI asked last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:02:57.99,Book,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Physical Training
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.68,0:03:00.26,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Ryugazaki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.00,0:03:02.53,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,You go to school by train?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:03.91,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.53,0:03:07.13,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, by the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.13,0:03:09.12,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to ask you a favor, as a classmate...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:10.96,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,I won't join the swim club.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:13.84,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? How did you know \Nbefore I said anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.84,0:03:15.63,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,It was easy enough to guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:16.30,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:19.23,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Considering the recruiting posters in your bag,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.23,0:03:23.68,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,and those swimsuit Iwatobi-chan straps \Nyou probably plan to give to new recruits.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.67,0:03:26.97,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,As I mentioned before,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.48,0:03:31.10,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,I already joined the track team.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:31.85,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.07,0:03:33.24,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:34.59,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,The school is the next station!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.99,0:03:39.11,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:41.53,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,He runs the last stretch every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:52.33,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I want to swim already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.12,0:03:55.33,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:57.65,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,We can swim here in the off-season?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:03:58.13,FlyerA,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,A free environment where you can \Nreinvent yourself at your pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:03:58.13,FlyerB,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Spring Recruitment Campaign
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:03:58.55,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:03:59.25,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:03.62,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking that schools like us
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.62,0:04:06.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,without indoor pools probably \Nuse facilities like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:07.30,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Gou-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.30,0:04:08.17,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Our super manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.17,0:04:10.39,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to call me Kou!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.28,0:04:12.82,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Haruka-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.73,0:04:17.56,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,How do we pay for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.97,0:04:20.21,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,With our club budget, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:21.15,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:24.54,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,This gym is pretty expensive to join.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:26.60,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,If our club budget will really cover that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:31.25,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,This is the real reason \Nwe started a swim club.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:32.79,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,That's probably what you're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:34.39,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.02,0:04:37.29,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,This means we can swim year round!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:39.67,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,That's not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.67,0:04:41.41,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.41,0:04:43.35,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,The school isn't going \Nto give that much money
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.35,0:04:48.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,to a brand-new club \Nwith no accomplishments.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:51.66,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,There is an aphorism from the Bible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:53.77,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,He who does not work, \Nneither shall he eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:56.81,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you're using that correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:04:58.31,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,You can't eat a pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.64,0:05:01.78,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,So we'll get the money if \Nwe deliver accomplishments?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:03.06,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.06,0:05:07.02,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,That's the best way to secure \Nlots of money for your club.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.02,0:05:08.03,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Accomplishments...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:11.41,Main,Makoto,0000,0000,0000,,So what if we can place \Nin a summer tournament?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:12.89,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,Your request might be approved
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.89,0:05:14.52,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,at the second term budget review meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.52,0:05:18.46,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,But you'll need at least four \Nswimmers to bolster your case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:19.51,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Swimmers...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:20.81,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}So it's meaningless if we \Ncan't find another member...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.61,0:05:22.92,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,One more...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:24.13,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,...and I can swim all I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:24.72,Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.53,0:05:26.30,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Haru?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.79,0:05:29.18,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Haru-chan sounds motivated now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:33.97,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Haru?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:39.48,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.85,0:05:41.29,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,That was a trick question.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:42.40,Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I thought the same—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:42.95,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.10,0:05:45.43,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.43,0:05:46.65,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,So join the swim club.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.48,0:05:48.95,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:50.32,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.65,0:05:51.85,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,It's hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.85,0:05:54.19,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,That's the best Haru can manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:55.91,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let it get to you, Haru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:59.79,Flyer,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Fun! Iwatobi Swim Club
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:02.85,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Should the posters be flashier?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.33,0:06:05.05,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.79,0:06:07.61,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Ryugazaki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.61,0:06:09.90,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.90,0:06:12.49,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,We can talk about swimming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.49,0:06:14.38,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,I have practice now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:15.39,Deodorizer,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,224)}Deodorizer
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:17.84,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,And there's nothing you can say
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.42,0:06:21.01,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,that will convince me to join the swim club.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:24.37,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Ryugazaki-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:27.35,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:29.53,Name,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Ryugazaki
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.18,0:06:33.25,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.25,0:06:33.92,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:36.79,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,I found the perfect person!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.19,0:06:38.52,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,The track team?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.52,0:06:40.04,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,He can't join us, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:41.24,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Look. Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:44.55,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,It's his fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:46.11,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Was he on the swim team in middle school?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.11,0:06:47.97,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Does he hold a record?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:49.41,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,It's his name!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.41,0:06:50.09,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,His name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:50.84,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:53.39,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,It's Ryugazaki Rei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:53.39,Name2,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Ryugazaki Rei
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:55.63,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,He's the same as us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.63,0:06:57.98,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,A boy with a girly name!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.98,0:06:59.14,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,That's your reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.55,0:07:02.78,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,But I have to agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.78,0:07:04.65,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Look at those deltoids...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.87,0:07:05.82,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,That's your reason?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.06,0:07:07.92,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,You really think those reasons are enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.92,0:07:09.53,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,My reason is very good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:10.57,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next, Ryugazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:10.86,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Mako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:11.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:12.16,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Go with your gut on these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.42,0:07:14.41,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it looks like he's about to jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:16.25,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Bar height: 4.20 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.25,0:07:17.49,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Set takeoff speed to {\i1}v{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.49,0:07:19.32,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Set acceleration to {\i1}a{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:20.41,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Gravity is {\i1}g{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:23.29,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,If the center of gravity after taking \Ninto account pole length is {\i1}h{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:24.34,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,then the angle of approach...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.16,0:07:37.35,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,His form was beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.37,0:07:40.59,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably a great diver.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.59,0:07:41.35,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.35,0:07:42.99,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,And his biceps are also beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.99,0:07:44.19,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all you care about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:46.15,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,I miscalculated the angle of approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:58.02,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Rei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:00.30,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Rei-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.53,0:08:05.08,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you can call me Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:06.41,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.41,0:08:08.25,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't that close.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:11.76,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,We can get closer once \Nyou join the swim club.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:13.12,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to join.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:17.76,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only interested in \Nsports that are beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:19.49,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Like track?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.49,0:08:20.22,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.44,0:08:24.55,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,It's a sport known for beautiful \Nevents such as pole vaulting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:28.90,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,You can attain the perfect form \Nthrough theory and calculation!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:32.01,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds too hard \Nfor me to understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.54,0:08:34.30,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,but you can be in both \Nclubs at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.77,0:08:37.42,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,You use your arm muscles \Nfor pole vaulting, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.42,0:08:39.14,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,So doesn't swimming sound perfect?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:40.70,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to join both.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.14,0:08:45.40,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,After all, humans evolved to live on land.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.40,0:08:51.67,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you go backwards \Nand play sports in water?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:54.11,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,It defies reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.11,0:08:58.51,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget that water has 12 to \N13 times the viscosity of air!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:00.26,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,No luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.26,0:09:02.10,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't say yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.45,0:09:04.18,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think Rei-chan likes water.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.49,0:09:05.87,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need anyone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.87,0:09:07.37,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let him in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.37,0:09:08.65,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,If you say that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.56,0:09:11.28,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,nobody will join!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:14.26,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to spend all winter \Nlifting weights and jogging!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.26,0:09:15.23,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay with that, Haru-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.23,0:09:16.50,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really okay with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.94,0:09:19.83,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:23.84,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,I think we need to ask Ama-chan \Nto strip down for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.84,0:09:24.86,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,That won't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.86,0:09:26.84,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,She said that she won't wear a swimsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.84,0:09:28.28,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Then we should reverse it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.28,0:09:29.33,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:33.53,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,If you join, you get to show \Noff your swimsuit to Ama-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:35.35,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Does anybody want that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.35,0:09:37.09,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, don't write that down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.15,0:09:41.43,Main,Ama,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:44.57,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.05,0:09:48.15,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:52.39,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like we'll be entering tournaments.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.85,0:09:54.57,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.12,0:09:58.49,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you end up racing Rin again
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:03.82,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,and beating him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:07.16,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Who told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.57,0:10:10.25,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,I happened to run into Coach \NSasabe the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:15.65,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,It's in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.58,0:10:17.69,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:20.46,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,He's swimming again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.23,0:10:22.14,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.29,0:10:29.13,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Bar height: 4.30 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.13,0:10:30.23,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Set takeoff speed to {\i1}v{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.64,0:10:32.89,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Leave {\i1}a{\i0}, acceleration, unchanged.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.89,0:10:34.91,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,But factor in the potential energy
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:37.21,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,from any shifts in the \Npole's center of gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:51.69,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Ryugazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:54.03,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Are you running calculations \Nin your head before jumping?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.74,0:10:58.00,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Your form is perfect,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.00,0:10:59.44,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,but that's all you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.44,0:11:01.19,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,You're too focused on the technical side.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.19,0:11:02.00,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.00,0:11:05.11,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that's your style,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.11,0:11:07.29,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,but you're not going to \Nimprove at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.68,0:11:15.63,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,I have good news for everyone today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:18.23,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Amazingly enough, I was able to schedule
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.23,0:11:19.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,a joint practice with Samezuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.49,0:11:20.97,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.73,0:11:23.94,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Did you ask Rin?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:26.74,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,My brother won't listen to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.74,0:11:29.12,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,so I went straight to their captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.61,0:11:31.00,Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,Joint practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.76,0:11:32.54,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.85,0:11:34.92,Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds great! Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.19,0:11:36.95,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,That's our super manager, Gou-cha—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.95,0:11:38.03,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kou.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.03,0:11:40.87,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,That means we have permission to swim
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.87,0:11:43.14,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,in Samezuka's indoor pool now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.79,0:11:44.89,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.23,0:11:47.14,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's a joint practice,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:50.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,we need to bring four \Nmembers at a minimum.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.01,0:11:54.81,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,That means we have to recruit a \Nnew member before the practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:57.73,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Especially since Gou-chan used her \Nsex appeal to get us this chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:11:59.19,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't use sex appeal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:12:00.21,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You didn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.21,0:12:01.70,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.79,0:12:06.05,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody told me there would \Nbe a joint practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.49,0:12:10.33,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,The captain made the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.80,0:12:14.34,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Your little sister is a member \Nof the Iwatobi swim club, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.34,0:12:15.94,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Their members are Nanase Haruka,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:17.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachibana Makoto, and Hazuki Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.29,0:12:20.56,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,They all have girly names—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:22.65,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:23.76,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:26.93,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I participated in that tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.53,0:12:28.86,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that was your
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.86,0:12:31.60,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,last tournament as a \Ngrade-schooler, Matsuoka-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.19,0:12:34.56,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,My team lost in the prelims.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.83,0:12:38.80,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,That race was amazing to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:48.99,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody's talking about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:55.47,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Rei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.98,0:12:58.65,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:01.55,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Can I run with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:06.01,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,If you can keep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.99,0:13:07.95,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:11.36,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,This brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.36,0:13:16.16,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,I used to run with Haru-chan to the \Nswimming club like this in grade school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.16,0:13:18.60,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Haru-chan always played \Nit cool and said,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.60,0:13:19.84,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,"If you can keep up."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.84,0:13:21.37,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this Haru-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.37,0:13:22.94,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you go this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.97,0:13:25.61,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:28.03,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,What do I want?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:31.13,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to join the swim club.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.13,0:13:35.30,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,We really need another member \Nbefore our joint practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:38.29,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Why does it have to be me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.33,0:13:43.26,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're a boy with a girly name?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.64,0:13:45.13,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,That's your reason?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:45.93,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.27,0:13:51.94,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,But the main reason is because \Nyou looked beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.94,0:13:52.71,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.71,0:13:54.12,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,When you were pole vaulting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.12,0:13:58.15,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Your jump looked really beautiful, Rei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:03.52,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:05.12,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,I was just
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:07.46,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,following theory and calculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.46,0:14:11.17,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,That's not something everybody can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.17,0:14:13.49,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,I suck at that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.90,0:14:19.83,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,So I want you to use theory and \Ncalculation to look good swimming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.43,0:14:21.34,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.82,0:14:24.86,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,A swimmer must flap his \Narms and legs underwater,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.86,0:14:28.47,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,while struggling to break \Nthe surface for a gasp of air.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.47,0:14:31.93,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,You can't look good while doing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:33.31,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:34.20,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:36.18,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Haru-chan is a beautiful swimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.55,0:14:40.52,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Haru-chan again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.01,0:14:42.82,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.90,0:14:44.82,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.34,0:14:47.54,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Haru-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.54,0:14:48.78,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Mako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:52.57,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Rei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.03,0:14:55.83,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,You're Haru-chan-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.22,0:14:58.87,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't put -chan {\i1}and{\i0} -san on my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:00.91,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Is something up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.56,0:15:05.26,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm willing to participate in your \Njoint practice as a trial member.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.26,0:15:06.17,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.53,0:15:08.55,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,But only on one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.61,0:15:13.39,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,I won't do any swimming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:15.56,samezuka,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Samezuka Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:18.06,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Indoor pools are so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:23.09,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Easy to see they're from a champion school...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.09,0:15:25.69,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,But ours are just as good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:25.69,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:28.67,Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, thanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:31.78,Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.17,0:15:32.94,Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.41,0:15:34.62,Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,You're Nanase-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.17,0:15:38.65,Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,You won a bunch of regional \Ntournaments in grade school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.65,0:15:39.27,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.27,0:15:40.71,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.27,0:15:40.71,Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I've heard a lot about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:42.11,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:42.45,Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You may not remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.11,0:15:43.33,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.45,0:15:46.85,Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}but when you won the Iwatobi \Nregional, I was second.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.85,0:15:50.17,Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I still remember how you beat \Nme on the 50 meter turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:50.17,Samezuka jacket,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Samezuka Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.83,0:15:48.68,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.23,0:15:50.17,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.73,0:15:53.32,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Gou, what are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.32,0:15:55.83,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Rin-chan! We get to swim together again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.83,0:15:57.06,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have fun today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:15:57.93,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Together?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:16:01.53,Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are a waste of my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:03.19,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.75,0:16:05.43,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,What's his problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.94,0:16:08.07,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, there's some history there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.39,0:16:12.15,Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking that you could practice \Nwith our first-years today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.47,0:16:13.36,Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:16.30,Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start with individual time trials.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:18.64,Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,You there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.64,0:16:20.13,Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,Get in your swimsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:21.09,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.09,0:16:22.33,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:24.63,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,He forgot to bring his swimsuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.73,0:16:25.97,Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.97,0:16:28.01,Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he here, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:32.00,Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,You can use one of our spare \Nswimsuits, so go get changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:32.80,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:33.87,Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nitori!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.87,0:16:34.97,Main,Ni,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.44,0:16:36.46,Main,Ni,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.46,0:16:37.80,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:39.14,Main,Ni,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:40.03,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:41.52,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.48,0:16:40.98,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You'll get in trouble again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:41.52,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm not swimming!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.41,0:16:45.62,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,The deal was that I wouldn't have to swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.62,0:16:46.73,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:49.13,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,These time trials are just for practice,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.13,0:16:51.06,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,so it doesn't matter if you're slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.06,0:16:53.06,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the issue!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.06,0:16:54.62,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Mako-chan's turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.62,0:16:56.26,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:02.54,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,So he's curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.46,0:17:06.44,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm up next.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:11.78,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.21,0:17:15.33,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.33,0:17:16.80,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Next swimmer, get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:21.39,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,You're up next, Ryugazaki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.87,0:17:22.63,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I'm not—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.63,0:17:23.39,Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, next swimmer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:25.02,Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,Move to the starting block!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:27.51,Main,Ni,0000,0000,0000,,Can the next person get over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.63,0:17:29.65,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:31.49,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,You might as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.48,0:17:35.95,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.08,0:17:39.43,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.13,0:17:41.24,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.75,0:17:44.91,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:48.69,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,It's about 50 centimeters from \Nthe surface to the starting block.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.69,0:17:49.71,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Set acceleration to {\i0}v{\i1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.71,0:17:51.51,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Set entry angle to {\i0}theta{\i1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.51,0:17:53.38,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Assuming that the water \Nviscosity is equal to {\i0}r{\i1}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.38,0:18:00.60,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Calculate the power I should \Nuse when kicking off...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.88,0:17:59.05,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.04,0:18:02.47,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,His form is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.57,0:18:05.31,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Set!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.82,0:18:07.77,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,What angle should my arms be at?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.30,0:18:14.57,Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:17.74,Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:25.77,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:27.60,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't come back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:29.08,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Um, this looks bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.40,0:18:33.58,Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,Is he okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:40.47,Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Whew...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:42.72,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,So Rei-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.21,0:18:44.72,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,You can't swim?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.36,0:18:46.73,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:48.07,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying it's my fault?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.07,0:18:50.69,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,I told you I wasn't going to swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.12,0:18:54.51,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,You should have said something earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.51,0:18:57.65,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't going to admit I couldn't swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.31,0:19:00.07,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,That would go against \Nmy sense of beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.97,0:19:03.19,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Rei-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.19,0:19:06.87,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,I'll clear things up with Samezuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:08.75,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about forcing you \Ninto this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.28,0:19:11.32,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Haru's turn to swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:17.74,Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:21.39,Main,Miko,0000,0000,0000,,Set!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.82,0:19:30.54,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,It's so beautiful to watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:31.85,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.38,0:19:34.56,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.75,0:19:39.57,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,See? I told you so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:41.32,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Haru-chan is an amazing swimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:43.55,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't use theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.21,0:19:45.58,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,No calculation, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.35,0:19:48.58,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,He has something much stronger
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.86,0:19:52.38,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,that I do not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.07,0:19:54.12,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Much stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.31,0:20:04.26,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Can I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.74,0:20:09.10,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Can I learn to swim like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.79,0:20:13.63,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't given up yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.63,0:20:14.56,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.42,0:20:17.90,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,But it looks like Rei-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.22,0:20:19.35,Main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Ryugazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.35,0:20:20.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:22.27,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,...is feeling much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.37,0:20:26.28,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,No theory... No calculation...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.10,0:20:28.99,Nar/Thought/Flashback,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Be free!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.68,0:20:42.05,Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.32,0:20:47.26,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,He fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:51.73,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? He's coming over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.65,0:20:57.23,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be like you, Nanase-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:00.13,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.13,0:21:01.74,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,I want that kind of freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:02.98,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,It's not freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:05.74,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,It's freestyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.32,0:21:08.15,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Fr-Freestyle...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.89,0:21:12.27,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I would like to formally
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.52,0:21:14.65,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,join the swim club!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.65,0:21:16.25,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.68,0:21:19.71,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to swim, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.07,0:21:21.31,Main,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,That's that, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.31,0:21:22.05,Main,Gou,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.86,0:21:24.16,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Haru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.16,0:21:28.15,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,However, you were the one who \Ninitially invited me to join.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.15,0:21:30.54,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,I expect you to take responsibility,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.34,0:21:32.67,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Nagisa-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:37.65,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! You can count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:39.10,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.71,0:23:14.94,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, so why can't you swim, Rei-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.94,0:23:15.75,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,That's a foolish question.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.75,0:23:17.61,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,The fluid mechanics of human \Nphysiology show that...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.61,0:23:19.55,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of that complicated stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.55,0:23:20.56,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.56,0:23:21.28,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.28,0:23:22.87,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,Haru-chan's fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.87,0:23:24.42,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,This is how you hold a carving knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.42,0:23:25.75,Main,Nagi,0000,0000,0000,,He's teaching him how \Nto make Iwatobi-chans.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.75,0:23:27.53,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,You're not done with those yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.53,0:23:29.63,Main,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Captive Butterfly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.59,0:23:35.97,NextEp,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(484,1)}Captive Butterfly!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.63,0:23:30.81,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,That's easy enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.81,0:23:33.60,Main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have the theory down by next week.
